N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 298.3 - Procedural and administrative regulations of the commissioner

State Regulations

Administrative Code of the City of New York, ยง
11-1943

The provisions of Articles 6 and 7 of this Chapter and

Chapter IX of this Title with respect to procedural and administrative
provisions for the State personal income tax applying to part VI of article 22
of the State Tax Law shall also be applicable to the procedures for and
administration of the nonresident earnings tax. Notes
